45:55.171 --> 46:00.181
<i>♪♪♪</i>

46:10.135 --> 46:15.145
<i>♪♪♪</i>

46:18.251 --> 46:20.087
What are you doing?

46:20.088 --> 46:22.124
Strolling.

46:22.125 --> 46:24.062
Like that?

46:24.063 --> 46:26.767
Does it make you uncomfortable?

46:26.768 --> 46:31.744
No. No, it doesn't.

46:31.745 --> 46:35.117
You just... consistently surprise me.

46:35.118 --> 46:36.921
(CHUCKLES)

46:36.922 --> 46:40.328
Yes, well, I surprise myself lately.

46:43.301 --> 46:46.206
I don't know exactly what
it is that I'm looking for,

46:46.207 --> 46:51.049
but I do know that I want
it to be passionate.

46:51.050 --> 46:53.988
I want to find a man where
there's real sexual...

46:53.989 --> 46:57.161
<i>♪♪♪</i>

46:57.162 --> 46:59.298
...chemistry.

46:59.299 --> 47:04.243
<i>♪♪♪</i>

47:12.994 --> 47:14.663
What are you doing?

47:14.664 --> 47:18.003
Bill, I-I thought that you
were in a session with Nancy.

47:18.004 --> 47:20.708
After this afternoon, I-I canceled

47:20.709 --> 47:22.679
the rest of the day's appointments.

47:22.680 --> 47:25.819
I was gonna check in
on Betty and Helen.

47:25.820 --> 47:27.622
Well, I should be going.

47:27.623 --> 47:29.827
You left something on the desk.

47:29.828 --> 47:31.697
You can open that later.

47:31.698 --> 47:34.403
What is it?

47:34.404 --> 47:36.908
Well, it's a... it's a surprise.

47:42.018 --> 47:44.656
(KEY JINGLES)

47:44.657 --> 47:48.197
It's our old room at the Park Chancery.

47:50.001 --> 47:54.009
I was hoping that you would
meet me there tonight.

47:57.015 --> 47:59.185
The Park Chancery?

47:59.186 --> 48:02.024
It's a time that we were at our best.

48:02.025 --> 48:04.863
The way we can be again.

48:04.864 --> 48:09.706
For godssake, Virginia...

48:09.707 --> 48:12.646
...I can't.

48:12.647 --> 48:13.681
Because...?

48:13.682 --> 48:14.750
Because you...

48:14.751 --> 48:17.756
<i>♪ somber music ♪</i>

48:17.757 --> 48:20.027
...you don't love me.

48:20.028 --> 48:22.599
What?

48:22.600 --> 48:24.235
That is preposterous.

48:24.236 --> 48:27.208
No, no, no, no, no.

48:27.209 --> 48:31.550
You don't. You just want me today.

48:31.551 --> 48:34.388
I don't know, maybe because
I-I've stopped pursuing you.

48:34.389 --> 48:38.096
Or be... because Dan is gone,
I'm the only option left.

48:38.097 --> 48:40.602
Or because it's just easier with
me because I'm always there.

48:40.603 --> 48:42.806
But what happens tomorrow,

48:42.807 --> 48:44.876
when you wake up and, uh,

48:44.877 --> 48:48.216
oh, you want someone else?

48:48.217 --> 48:50.588
Bill, that's not going to happen.

48:50.589 --> 48:54.295
I don't trust you, Virginia.

48:54.296 --> 48:56.065
I can't. (KEY JINGLES)

48:56.066 --> 48:57.936
Ever again.

48:57.937 --> 49:02.913
<i>♪♪♪</i>

49:11.731 --> 49:14.135
Uh, you didn't have to come.

49:14.136 --> 49:15.638
(EXHALES DEEPLY)

49:15.639 --> 49:18.878
Well, I'm actually here
for the cafeteria food.

49:18.879 --> 49:22.384
I do love those Jell-O squares.

49:22.385 --> 49:25.658
Is everything all right with you, Doc?

49:25.659 --> 49:27.495
Of course.

49:27.496 --> 49:29.766
So has Barton been out?

49:29.767 --> 49:33.239
(SIGHS) Last update
was, uh, an hour ago.

49:33.240 --> 49:35.778
They were still waiting
on the anesthesiologist.

49:35.779 --> 49:38.083
Right.

49:38.084 --> 49:40.488
(SIGHS)

49:40.489 --> 49:43.661
Um, I called Helen's folks.

49:43.662 --> 49:46.967
Oh, what did they say?

49:46.968 --> 49:50.140
Turns out they think
Helen would've married

49:50.141 --> 49:52.779
the captain of the football
team if I hadn't lured her

49:52.780 --> 49:55.786
into a life of sin and debauchery.

49:58.825 --> 50:01.864
So I said, "Fine. Fine, but blame me.

50:01.865 --> 50:05.070
Blame me for everything. Don't
punish your own daughter.

50:05.071 --> 50:07.842
Your own grandchild.
What are you thinking?"

50:07.843 --> 50:10.882
You said all that?

50:10.883 --> 50:13.555
After they hung up, but yeah.

50:18.230 --> 50:21.737
It... it's hard to see, sometimes.

50:21.738 --> 50:23.507
See what?

50:23.508 --> 50:27.582
Well, they don't see what
you and Helen have done.

50:27.583 --> 50:30.121
That you've made a family.

50:35.097 --> 50:38.704
(BABY GURGLING)

50:38.705 --> 50:41.710
Is he okay? Is he healthy?

50:41.711 --> 50:45.083
She is perfect. Congratulations.

50:45.084 --> 50:48.256
She.

50:48.257 --> 50:50.495
Betty has to see her.

50:50.496 --> 50:52.164
We can send Betty to the nursery.

50:52.165 --> 50:53.767
We're taking your daughter there now

50:53.768 --> 50:57.107
while we clean you up and
make you comfortable.

50:57.108 --> 51:01.783
But can Betty sit with me
first, in here, please?

51:01.784 --> 51:04.723
<i>♪ soft music ♪</i>

51:04.724 --> 51:06.125
Please.

51:06.126 --> 51:11.135
<i>♪♪♪</i>

51:11.136 --> 51:14.643
We paid for one
Butterfinger three times.

51:14.644 --> 51:16.547
- Miss DiMello?
- Y-yes, is it over?

51:16.548 --> 51:17.782
Is... is everything okay?

51:17.783 --> 51:18.884
The baby's fine.

51:18.885 --> 51:21.723
Oh, my God. Thank you.

51:21.724 --> 51:24.328
Miss Schiff has requested your
presence in the delivery room.

51:24.329 --> 51:25.831
Dr. Scully agreed.

51:25.832 --> 51:27.435
Actually, I'm Dr. Masters.

51:27.436 --> 51:28.938
Dr. Scully is part of my practice.

51:28.939 --> 51:30.943
I'll escort Miss DiMello back.

51:35.919 --> 51:39.024
Hey.

51:39.025 --> 51:41.029
She's gorgeous.

51:43.033 --> 51:44.603
SCULLY: Increase the sedation.

51:44.604 --> 51:46.707
WOMAN: It's not
cauterizing, Dr. Scully.

51:46.708 --> 51:48.444
Systolic?

51:48.445 --> 51:49.546
WOMAN: 240.

51:49.547 --> 51:51.315
WOMAN: Pressure keeps dropping.

51:51.316 --> 51:53.454
<i>♪ tense somber music ♪</i>

51:53.455 --> 51:54.990
You want some help, Barton?

51:54.991 --> 51:56.960
Scrub up, Bill.

51:56.961 --> 52:01.903
<i>♪♪♪</i>

52:01.904 --> 52:03.507
MASTERS: You need more exposure.

52:03.508 --> 52:05.076
BARTON: I can't see the
vessels to suture.

52:05.077 --> 52:08.082
MASTERS: Three more bags of
platelets and another clamp.

52:08.083 --> 52:10.988
Hey, hey, my Grandma Pearl always says

52:10.989 --> 52:12.825
that... that you shouldn't
rush a baby's name

52:12.826 --> 52:16.132
'cause a baby practically
names herself.

52:16.133 --> 52:20.373
And I had named our baby Harry.

52:20.374 --> 52:21.710
Am I sick?

52:21.711 --> 52:23.614
Nope, you're not sick.

52:23.615 --> 52:25.451
You're just, um...

52:25.452 --> 52:27.822
this is all normal
after you have a baby.

52:27.823 --> 52:32.330
Doc Scully's taking
real good care of you.

52:32.331 --> 52:34.803
- Something's wrong.
- No, nothing's wrong.

52:34.804 --> 52:37.240
Nothing's wrong. You're
in the delivery room

52:37.241 --> 52:41.248
and our baby's napping in the nursery.

52:41.249 --> 52:43.352
You're okay.

52:43.353 --> 52:44.756
Everything's okay.

52:44.757 --> 52:47.662
We're gonna be a family, remember?

52:47.663 --> 52:50.166
Remember? (SNIFFS)

52:50.167 --> 52:53.907
Helen, stay with me.

52:53.908 --> 52:56.913
(LABORED BREATHING)

52:56.914 --> 52:59.351
<i>♪♪♪</i>

52:59.352 --> 53:02.057
I want my mom.

53:02.058 --> 53:06.900
<i>♪♪♪</i>

53:06.901 --> 53:10.073
I want my mom.

53:10.074 --> 53:15.084
<i>♪♪♪</i>

53:17.890 --> 53:21.195
(CHOKING UP)

53:21.196 --> 53:26.206
<i>♪♪♪</i>

53:36.226 --> 53:41.236
<i>♪♪♪</i>

53:50.589 --> 53:52.592
We're gonna have to take her now.

53:52.593 --> 53:57.603
<i>♪♪♪</i>

54:08.558 --> 54:13.568
<i>♪♪♪</i>

54:15.104 --> 54:17.207
Guy called me. I came
as soon as I could.

54:17.208 --> 54:20.915
<i>♪♪♪</i>

54:20.916 --> 54:22.785
Oh, God, what?

54:22.786 --> 54:25.824
It's called D. I. C.

54:25.825 --> 54:29.298
It means the blood just won't clot.

54:29.299 --> 54:32.939
We went through 16 bags.

54:32.940 --> 54:34.776
No matter how much we transfused,

54:34.777 --> 54:38.282
or sutured, or...

54:38.283 --> 54:41.756
<i>♪♪♪</i>

54:41.757 --> 54:45.831
She just kept bleeding...

54:45.832 --> 54:49.839
...until there was no blood left.

54:49.840 --> 54:54.849
<i>♪♪♪</i>

54:54.850 --> 54:56.486
Is Betty...?

54:56.487 --> 54:59.492
Betty's with her.

54:59.493 --> 55:04.436
<i>♪♪♪</i>

55:17.963 --> 55:20.667
<i>♪♪♪</i>

55:20.668 --> 55:23.673
(BABY CRYING)

55:23.674 --> 55:28.684
<i>♪♪♪</i>

55:32.224 --> 55:33.225
(BABY CRYING)

55:33.226 --> 55:36.198
(NO AUDIBLE DIALOGUE)

55:36.199 --> 55:40.006
<i>♪♪♪</i>

55:40.007 --> 55:41.476
The grandparents made it clear.

55:41.477 --> 55:43.312
Family only.

